title: Marcus Miller - Afrodeezia
description:
Title: Afrodeezia
Artist: Marcus Miller
Genre: Fusion Jazz
Year: 2015
Label: Blue Note
Format: FLAC (lossless)
Duration: 1:05:02
Total Size: 606MB (391MB music and metadata, 214MB covers and booklet)

Track Listing:
1  - Hylife
2  - B's River
3  - Preacher's Kid (Song for William H)
4  - We Were There
5  - Papa Was a Rolling Stone
6  - I Still Believe
7  - Son of Macbeth
8  - Prism (Interlude)
9  - Xtraordinary
10 - Water Dancer
11 - I Can't Breathe

_________________

Encoding details:
  Channels    - Stereo
  Sample Rate - 44100Hz
  Encoded with CUETools FLACCL 2.1.5 with settings: -11 --lax

Booklet and cover were scanned with a poor desktop scanner at 600dpi (it is a normal CD jewel case). They were encoded in PNG with optipng with settings: -o7 -strip all

I went to his concert and got this CD there. I let him sign it. I had seen that this wasn't available on either KAT or TPB, so I decided to make a good copy of it and spread it. TPB was how I found Marcus and became a fan. I hope you take a good listen!
